 <h2>White Dragonscale Cloak Quest</h2><br><br>This quest is pretty strait forward, almost a formality, to turn "White Dragon Hide" into this cloak:<br><br><iframe src="http://www.eqmages.com/itemstat1.php?id=11603" width="420" height="220" scrolling="no" frameborder="0"></iframe><br><br>Really, the dragon hide might as well be the actual cloak. :)<br><br><br><b>Karam Darkforge</b> is in Kaladim at about 4100,900. To make the cloak you must give him the following:<br><br><iframe src="http://www.eqmages.com/itemstat1.php?id=30353" width="420" height="220" scrolling="no" frameborder="0"></iframe><br><iframe src="http://www.eqmages.com/itemstat1.php?id=14703" width="420" height="220" scrolling="no" frameborder="0"></iframe><br><iframe src="http://www.eqmages.com/itemstat1.php?id=9240" width="420" height="220" scrolling="no" frameborder="0"></iframe><br><br><br>The first two items are simply jewelry combines, though both trivial above 250. For the first you need an enchanted bar of velium and a diamond, for the second an enchanted bar of platinum and a black sapphire.<br><br>The third item is the real part of this quest, a dragon hide that can only be obtained off <a href='http://eqbeastiary.allakhazam.com/search.shtml?id=5034'>Gorenaire</a> or <a href='http://eqbeastiary.allakhazam.com/search.shtml?id=2620'>Vox</a><br><br><br><br></center><b><u>Zone Information:</u></b><br><br><a href='http://www.eqmages.com' onClick='moblist(52); return false;'>Kaladim South mob list</a><br>
<a href='http://www.eqmages.com' onClick='questlist(52); return false;'>Kaladim South quest list</a><br><a href='http://eqatlas.com/kaladim.html'>Kaladim South Map</a><br><br><b><u>Comments/Feedback:</u></b><br><br><i><b>Arremis</b> says:</i><br>It was mentioned this quest was for levels 40-65. I don't see how this is true, given the only NO DROP item in this quest is off of level 55 and 60 raid mobs. Correct me if I'm wrong here, but is it even possible for a level 40 to do this quest? If so, then how?<br><br><i><b>Anonymous</b> says:</i><br>VoX can only be done by level 52 or lower<br><br><form action='rate.php' method='post' name='rate'>
